[ABC, DEF]
[GHI, JKL]
DEF
```
Contrast the following using the same data and see what happens when you try to get an `&quot;Integer&quot;` from a list in the array.
```
@SuppressWarnings(&quot;unchecked&quot;)
List&lt;Integer&gt;[] array = results.stream().toArray(List[]::new);
